Date:   Wed Sep 28 15:37:51 2011 +0000

    k800i.py use new find syntax

Author: Frederic Baguelin <fba@digital-forensic.org>
Date:   Wed Sep 28 15:43:28 2011 +0000

    * Modules: web viewer
    ** deactivate javascript and activate private browsing

